6#define __FP_FRAC_ADD_4(r3,r2,r1,r0,x3,x2,x1,x0,y3,y2,y1,y0) \
7 __asm__ ("add{l} {%11,%3|%3,%11}\n\t" \
8 "adc{l} {%9,%2|%2,%9}\n\t" \
9 "adc{l} {%7,%1|%1,%7}\n\t" \
10 "adc{l} {%5,%0|%0,%5}" \

12 "=&r" ((USItype) (r2)), \
13 "=&r" ((USItype) (r1)), \
14 "=&r" ((USItype) (r0)) \
15 : "%0" ((USItype) (x3)), \

41 : "=r" ((USItype) (r3)), \

55 "sbb{l} {%6,%1|%1,%6}\n\t" \

58 "=&r" ((USItype) (r1)), \
59 "=&r" ((USItype) (r0)) \

66#define __FP_FRAC_ADDI_4(x3,x2,x1,x0,i) \
